Modify a Tadpole Curve

View and modify tadpole Data.

On the Workflows tab, select Tadpole Data. The View and Modify Tadpole Data will open.

In the Select a Definition, select the tadpole definition containing the data you wish the view/modify. The grid below will populate with data accordingly.

To modify the data, click on the desired table field, edit the data and hit Return on your keyboard.

Click Exit to update any changes.

Tip. Quickly toggle to the Tadpole Definitions by clicking Definitions at the bottom of the dialog box. When in Tadpole Definitions, revert to the View and Modify Tadpole Data dialog box by clicking Data.
